#: functions.php:1697
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The \"url\" property in your %1$s shortcode appears to contain HTML tags; "
"most likely your URL has been turned into a clickable link. Your calendar "
"may not display properly as a result. Please remove the clickable link in "
"the shortcode."
msgstr ""
